revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yearwoods}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yearwood'' is the 10429<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 3085 individuals. ''Yearwood'' is most common among White (50.15%) and Black/African American (38.8%) individuals.
